ClaimCo
├─ Tabs
├─ Home
│   ├─ Daily Summary
│   │   ├─ Shows pending, submitted, and approved claims for the day
│   │   ├─ Alerts for missing receipts or upcoming deadlines
│   │   └─ Quick link to add new claim
│   │
│   ├─ Claim Insights
│   │   ├─ Weekly and monthly expense summary (by tag/project)
│   │   ├─ Pie chart of category breakdown (e.g. travel, meals, tools)
│   │   └─ Claim limits or policy reminders
│   │
│   ├─ Smart Notifications
│   │   ├─ Nudges for unsubmitted drafts or rejected claims
│   │   └─ Reminder for end-of-month wrap-up
│   │
│   └─ Tips & Resources
│       ├─ Guide on claim policy, document requirements
│       └─ Submission tips (e.g., preferred formats, max limits)
├─ Claim
│   ├─ Receipt Scanner
│   │   ├─ Snap photo or upload file
│   │   └─ Use OCR to extract date, merchant, amount
│   │
│   ├─ Claim Form
│   │   ├─ Auto-filled from OCR, manually editable
│   │   ├─ Fields: date, merchant, category, amount, remarks, tag
│   │   └─ Upload supporting files (invoice, email, doc ID)
│   │
│   ├─ Submit Claim
│   │   ├─ Select approver (auto-routed by tag or department)
│   │   └─ Confirmation and soft copy summary
│   │
│   └─ Claim Drafts
│       ├─ Save incomplete claims
│       └─ Resume or discard later
│
├─ Track
│   ├─ Claim Timeline
│   │   ├─ Status flow: Submitted → In Review → Approved → Paid
│   │   └─ Visual indicator for each stage and last update timestamp
│   │
│   ├─ Filter & Search
│   │   ├─ Filter by tag, date range, status
│   │   └─ Quick search by merchant or keyword
│   │
│   ├─ View Claim Details
│   │   ├─ Receipt preview, notes, attached files
│   │   └─ Who approved, when, any comments
│   │
│   └─ Export
│       ├─ Generate PDF or CSV summary for selected claims
│       └─ Email/export to finance or personal records
│
├─ Profile
│   ├─ Personal Info
│   │   ├─ Name, department, contact details
│   │   └─ Preferred approver or cost center
│   │
│   ├─ Claim Settings
│   │   ├─ Set default tags, default remarks
│   │   └─ Enable/disable OCR auto-fill
│   │
│   ├─ Integrations
│   │   ├─ Connect Google Drive for receipt storage
│   │   └─ Auto-sync submitted claims to Google Sheet
│   │
│   └─ Help and Support
│       ├─ FAQ and claim policy docs
│       ├─ Report issue or contact finance
│       └─ Feedback and improvement suggestions
